				<div class="footer-col">
					<h3>Contact</h3>
					<p>📞 +91 9998569069</p>
					<p>📍 290 - Gopal Nagar OPP, G.H.BORAD , Pandesara, Surat, Gujarat 394210</p>
				</div>

				<div class="footer-col">
